I have to leave.

18
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,400
Wait.

19
00:01:51,580 --> 00:01:54,380
I just want you to sign it before you leave.

20
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:57,240
 What should I do? 

21
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:02,079
 Why are you ears so red? 

22
00:02:03,319 --> 00:02:05,619
 You're a bit close to me. 

23
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:11,699
 I guess I have to try this. 

24
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:52,600
President Fu, look...

25
00:02:53,340 --> 00:02:56,339
Is it okay to sign it this way?

26
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,779
President Fu?

27
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:25,680
President Fu,

28
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:30,820
I hope we can cooperate happily.

29
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:36,579
I have to go.

30
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:04,319
President Fu.

31
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,039
You seem bedazzled.

32
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:10,339
Well, is there something between you and Miss Penny?

33
00:04:10,339 --> 00:04:11,379
Don't you have work to do?

34
00:04:11,379 --> 00:04:14,039
Well, I'm just verbalizing your thoughts.

35
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:16,240
I've been busy seeking information about Miss Penny.

36
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:19,159
If that's the case, then I won't say anything.

37
00:04:19,159 --> 00:04:20,660
Come back.

38
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,540
Say it.

39
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:24,639
Miss Penny's birthday is two weeks away.

40
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:28,239
Shouldn't you prepare gifts in advance and put up a good show?

41
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:34,700
Why would I ever give her a present?

42
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:55,919
Thank you for helping me pick out a present today.

43
00:04:55,919 --> 00:04:58,999
I can tell that you really care about this female friend.

44
00:04:58,999 --> 00:05:00,960
I'm curious about why she is so special.

45
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,800
She's a designer.

46
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:05,240
Very talented yet very low-key.

47
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,800
She's strong but also can be vulnerable.

48
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:10,160
She's kind but always keeps her distance.

49
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:13,519
I can't help but want to know more about her.

50
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:16,720
Then what does she like?

51
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:19,519
Whatever you like will surely please her.

52
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:28,299
I've been eyeing this Sunshine necklace for such a long time.

53
00:05:28,299 --> 00:05:29,920
It isn't on the market.

54
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:32,699
I didn't expect to see it here.

55
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,419
I'll take this then.

56
