It really suits you.

67
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:02,839
 Yancheng, I'm back. 

68
00:07:05,799 --> 00:07:07,560
Chuqing. 
    

69
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:11,040
Long time no see.

70
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:13,580
I came to see you as soon as I got back. Surprised?

71
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:17,039
Why didn't you tell me earlier? I could've sent Qi Chen to pick you up.

72
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,699
This is?

73
00:07:19,699 --> 00:07:23,800
Hello, I'm Penny, the designer for President Fu's villa.

74
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,739
Xiao Chuqing.

75
00:07:25,739 --> 00:07:28,040
Yancheng, have you forgotten I'm a designer, too.

76
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,559
You didn't tell me about the renovations.

77
00:07:29,559 --> 00:07:31,680
You're so busy. How can I bother you?

78
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:34,320
Besides I like Penny's design style very much.

79
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:37,560
Then I should learn from Miss Penny.

80
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,680
You flatter me, Miss Xiao.

81
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:41,519
By the way, Yancheng,

82
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:44,160
I want a welcome banquet today.

83
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,680
I can hold it at your place, right?

84
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,160
Sure.

85
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:51,299
Please join us, Miss Penny.

86
00:07:51,299 --> 00:07:53,380
Thanks for inviting me, but I won't come.

87
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:55,360
We have many friends who need to decorate their home.

88
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,519
Come and meet them.

89
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:58,000
Come.

90
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,859
I also want to introduce you to more people.

91
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:03,299
Okay.

92
00:08:03,299 --> 00:08:06,360
It's better to accept deferentially than to decline courteously.

93
00:08:16,859 --> 00:08:19,639
Chuqing, three years ago, when Fu Yan cheng got married,

94
00:08:19,639 --> 00:08:21,759
you went abroad angrily and since then, you've refused to see him.

95
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:24,000
Are you back because you've moved on

96
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:28,160
or because he's getting a divorce from that woman from a humble family?

97
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,360
Miss Xiao.

98
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:33,340
Penny, I'm glad you could come.

99
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,580
Penny.

100
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:39,399
That dress suits you very well.

101
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:41,180
Thank you, President Fu.

102
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:44,520
Yancheng, my mom is here.

103
00:08:58,519 --> 00:09:01,959
 Oh no. I can't let her see me! 

104
00:09:12,499 --> 00:09:15,600
- Yancheng. 
 - Madam Bai, long time no see.

105
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,120
Do you mind if we have a word?

106
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,720
This way, please.

107
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:20,320
Okay.

108
00:09:28,479 --> 00:09:31,859
I'm sorry, President Fu. I felt a little dizzy just now.

109
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:35,159
Chuqing, I'm sorry.

110
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,440
It's okay.

111
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:39,360
- I'm sorry about the stain on your dress. 
 - It's okay.

112
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:42,460
You were invited by Yan Cheng. I can't be the killjoy.

113
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:44,039
Let me take you to deal with it.

114
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:46,780
- Don't bother. 
 - It's okay, let's go.

115
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:54,060
This is a dress my friend just gave me. I haven't worn it yet.

116
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:56,720
We're about the same size. Why don't you wear it.

117
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:59,240
It's fine. I'll just dry my dress.

118
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,480
Yancheng's friend is my friend, too.

119
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,200
You don't have to be so polite.

120
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,759
Don't worry. I'll keep an eye out for you.

121
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:06,479
Just go ahead.

122
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:27,080
Penny, though we just met each other,

123
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,120
you seem quite easy on the eyes.

124
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:31,899
