125
00:10:31,899 --> 00:10:34,139
I don't know if you mind.

126
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:36,240
Thank you for trusting me.

127
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:38,200
Just tell me about it.

128
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:41,600
Three years ago, I did go abroad because of Yancheng.

129
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,840
That was because he broke his promise.

130
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:47,740
Though he said he was forced to do so, I still didn't forgive him.

131
00:10:47,740 --> 00:10:50,600
But some time ago, he said he was getting a divorce

132
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:53,399
and asked me to give him a second chance.

133
00:10:53,399 --> 00:10:58,080
Penny, do you think I should give him another chance?

134
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:00,159
Since you have this question,

135
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:03,320
I guess when you asked me, you already had an answer.

136
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:05,879
So, you don't have to ask my opinion.

137
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:10,120
Secondly... I'm just a business partner with President Fu.

138
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:12,299
It isn't appropriate to pry into his personal matters.

139
00:11:12,299 --> 00:11:14,459
Please forgive me.

140
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:18,799
No wonder Yancheng appreciates you, Penny.

141
00:11:18,799 --> 00:11:20,919
You're very diplomatic.

142
