147
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:02,420
You know about Sunlight, too?

148
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,919
My best friend gave it to me.

149
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:06,719
Isn't it pretty?

150
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,979
So beautiful.

151
00:12:11,679 --> 00:12:14,220
